WK2D3: Hard days make a hard man 🥵 5lb plates come in early next week so I can finally use the correct weight instead of having to over/under shoot each session 😗 
Overload Squat (about +65 in chains): 315x4@7, 365x4@8, 385x4@9, 355x4@backdown 
TNG Bench: 225x5@7, 230x5@8, 245x5@misgrooved9, 230x5x2@backdowns
